\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {7}{\ignorespaces FTL threshold sensitivity analysis across four operating points (540, 600, 720, 840 minutes). Panel (a) shows feasibility dramatically drops below 600 min. Panel (b) reveals profit trade-off: relaxed thresholds gain +11--23\% but at operational cost. Panel (c) demonstrates that only the 600-min choice stays within the sub-5-second requirement for real-time dispatch.}}{38}{figure.caption.24}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:ftl_sensitivity}{{7}{38}{FTL threshold sensitivity analysis across four operating points (540, 600, 720, 840 minutes). Panel (a) shows feasibility dramatically drops below 600 min. Panel (b) reveals profit trade-off: relaxed thresholds gain +11--23\% but at operational cost. Panel (c) demonstrates that only the 600-min choice stays within the sub-5-second requirement for real-time dispatch}{figure.caption.24}{}}
