\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {8}{\ignorespaces QIGA convergence advantage quantified over 20 independent runs and 200 generations. Panel (a) shows median convergence (thick lines) with individual runs (thin, faded). QIGA achieves stable 5.3\% improvement by generation 100, while classical GA plateaus at 2\% and GA+elitism reaches 3.5\%. Panel (b) provides box-plot distributions at key generational milestones, confirming QIGA's superiority in both mean and variance reduction.}}{39}{figure.caption.25}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:convergence}{{8}{39}{QIGA convergence advantage quantified over 20 independent runs and 200 generations. Panel (a) shows median convergence (thick lines) with individual runs (thin, faded). QIGA achieves stable 5.3\% improvement by generation 100, while classical GA plateaus at 2\% and GA+elitism reaches 3.5\%. Panel (b) provides box-plot distributions at key generational milestones, confirming QIGA's superiority in both mean and variance reduction}{figure.caption.25}{}}
